items.description: Boeing's (BA) second quarter jet deliveries marked the company's highest quarterly deliveries number since 2023. Robinhood's (HOOD) new tokenized US stocks and private company stakes face scrutiny in the European Union under Lithuania's banking regulations. Check out Yahoo Finance's interview with Robinhood CEO and chairman, Vlad Tenev, here. Datadog (DDOG) was downgraded by Guggenheim analysts to Sell from Neutral, citing concerns about the impact of OpenAI's (OPAI.PVT) shift away from the company. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination here.
